duties_responsibilities.duty: Thorough understanding and proficiency in executing the complete landscape architecture design process, from client onboarding through preliminary design, design development, and construction development.
Create high-quality digital landscape plans and review all design development, construction documents, and specifications for quality control.
Navigate CA building codes and local municipality zoning ordinances.
Engage in the continual development and improvement of design and management systems.
Manage project timelines & complexities and help keep the team on track and abreast of deadlines.
Maintain current LandFX experience and proficiency in other mandatory software.

education_certification.credential: Bachelor's degree in Landscape Architecture, Architecture, or a related field (Master's preferred)
